						Class Child Ref Key: 24
						Class ChildKey: 8
						Class: clsfrmQueryStockItems
						Property Template:
						Class DLL Name:
						Display Settings
							Window Location and Size
								Left:   Class Default
								Top:    2.135"
								Width:  Class Default
								Width Editable? Class Default
								Height: 1.792"
								Height Editable? Class Default
